,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T22:59:45.000Z","msg":"叉 油雞 正到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35e191d2ef7f6ad8169a72f99f251ae5e635b0d","tid":759632,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2216332973a385ecab1a80337e428970eb289281","tid":759632,"uid":192176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T19:42:29.000Z","msg":"識食一定係叉燒燒鴨飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鴨皮最緊要脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再叫碟蠔油炒菜芯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T23:43:12.000Z","msg":"但腩仔可以同叉燒一戰"},{"pid":"37c9c0f115827bd3db147426775f36f7a583dda1","tid":759632,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee732508792eb8b2c44af415624e146ed3655874","tid":759632,"uid":138725,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T21:06:49.000Z","msg":"外國呢邊好興叉燒腩燒鴨三拼<br />\n搞到返香港食唔返雙拼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T23:46:25.000Z","msg":"加錢咪有三拼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dbac9b290437342b2d4f7132b65d26b55f6e443","tid":759632,"uid":3068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T23:53:51.000Z","msg":"肥燶叉燒燒肉飯多汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f99bb14e0cc6d173f6f34fa614ab0ff8548f47","tid":759632,"uid":110734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T23:56:01.000Z","msg":"切雞燒肉"},{"pid":"aac896e84ace0ba655fd08279e03a855ee873612","tid":759632,"uid":110734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:06:13.000Z","msg":"生活咗咁多年都好唔理解叉燒有乜好食，除非食好靚個的叉燒，一般街買個種都好少蜜糖，有時直情冇，肉又實，有少肥個的好食，但舊肉個口感真係好難頂，如果鐘意少肥嘅有層次嘅口感會簡燒肉，加上又有脆皮，一次過滿足哂三種風格。<br />\n<br />\n切雞嚟講塊皮就有燒肉中間肥肉個種彈牙感，肉質較為軟，雞油又香，易入口，送飯一流，又大大舊。<br />\n<br />\n配料方面有 唔識寫 蔥，將雞嘅鮮味帶出嚟，另外燒肉個中式辣醬同切雞都好夾，送飯辣得嚟燒肉個脆皮又可以喺嘴裏面爆發，係一碗好好味嘅切雞燒肉飯。"},{"pid":"938ccf1a2caffd17887d6aeb4b53fb92bc2added","tid":759632,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:09:15.000Z","msg":"絕大部分街市燒味鋪都好肥 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76f13795ac7a75710fe4b540682619805f84521","tid":759632,"uid":192176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"938ccf1a2caffd17887d6aeb4b53fb92bc2added","tid":759632,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:09:15.000Z","msg":"絕大部分街市燒味鋪都好肥 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:10:46.000Z","msg":"燒味少肥先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0596f1e43a385eeb69eb977edf98f5d74d63eec8","tid":759632,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:16:37.000Z","msg":"排骨"},{"pid":"37fc8621b468fcbaa2ae44f1a71641c69c38c126","tid":759632,"uid":1600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:33:02.000Z","msg":"乳豬燒鵝飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea092fa91ebfa6134d0ef90285e70462ebd6abd","tid":759632,"uid":192176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37fc8621b468fcbaa2ae44f1a71641c69c38c126","tid":759632,"uid":1600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:33:02.000Z","msg":"乳豬燒鵝飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:18:01.000Z","msg":"好豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2933e4e0b9b3b88dd45575bca221461e22eb597","tid":759632,"uid":1600,"like":0,"d